title: love (wip)
lyrics:
There's multiple types of love
I think the nicest kind is, of course, is, the deepest kind
I think I've found it, but it's not...
It like something that's not constant
It comes and goes, for me at least
I still love people I'm not with

It just transforms into a different kind

It’s just my dumb opinion i don’t know anything

But that's cool, I like not knowing

I think life would be dull if you knew everything

I cherish everything that feels real at least at the moment

Because I think we live in a world where a lot of things are not...

Very real
